==================
Boost Build Notes
==================

Home: http://www.boost.org/

Download: http://www.boost.org/users/history/

License: Boost Software License

./bootstrap.sh

./b2  stage (or install)  \
    toolset=gcc  \
    cflags="$CFLAGS"  \
    cxxflags="$CXXFLAGS"  \
    variant=release  \
    link=shared  \
    threading=multi  \
    --build-dir="$work_dir"  \
    --stagedir="$work_dir"  \
    --with-system  \
    --with-thread  \
    ...

Now build libraries for dyninst: atomic, chrono, date_time,
filesystem, system, thread, timer.

The full boost package is quite large (70 Meg tar file, 540 Meg
unpacked).  The boost-headers tar file is the original tar file minus
the doc, libs, status and tools subdirectories.

